authors: Karen Barrow The New York Times
description: Every fall, Well goes vegetarian, offering delicious no-meat recipes for your holiday table from some of your favorite chefs and cookbook authors.
title: Well’s Vegetarian Thanksgiving 2012
title_page: Well’s Vegetarian Thanksgiving 2012 - Interactive Feature - NYTimes.com
text: Every fall, Well goes vegetarian for Thanksgiving , taking the meaty bird off the table to make room for a spectacular array of vegetarian soups, sides, main courses, salads and desserts. So get ready to save a turkey and savor the flavors of the fall harvest. Every day until Thanksgiving, we will add more vegetarian recipes for your holiday table. Click on a photo to learn more about each recipe.
